{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"tool_use_id": "chatcmpl-tool-9fe39a11e3e1cb69", "type": "tool_result", "content": "# F5-TTS: A Fairytaler that Fakes Fluent and Faithful Speech with Flow Matching\narXiv: 2410.06885\nAuthors: Yushen Chen, Zhikang Niu, Ziyang Ma, Keqi Deng, Chunhui Wang, Jian Zhao, Kai Yu, Xie Chen\nYear: 2024 | Venue: \nTopic: tts_vc\nStatus: reading\n\nContributions:\n  1. Introduces F5-TTS, a fully non-autoregressive text-to-speech system based on flow matching with a Diffusion Transformer (DiT) that eliminates the need for complex designs like duration models, text encoders, and phoneme alignment.\n  2. Improves text-speech alignment and model robustness by leveraging ConvNeXt V2 blocks to refine text representation before concatenation with speech features.\n  3. Proposes an inference-time Sway Sampling strategy for flow steps that significantly enhances generation performance and efficiency without requiring model retraining.\n  4. Achieves faster training and a highly efficient inference Real-Time Factor (RTF) of 0.15, outperforming existing state-of-the-art diffusion-based TTS models.\n  5. Demonstrates highly natural and expressive zero-shot ability, seamless code-switching capability, and speed control efficiency when trained on a public 100K hours multilingual dataset.\n\nTags: TTS, TTS/架构-NAR-Flow, TTS/功能-DiT, TTS/功能-多语言, TTS/控制-参考语音, TTS/功能-快速生成", "is_error": false}]}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "bda99c47-f934-4eb4-b83d-e7d7ba9a9f3d", "uuid": "64917d79-d679-4107-a530-bde638ff5169", "timestamp": "2026-07-11T12:42:33.200Z", "tool_use_result": {"stdout": "# F5-TTS: A Fairytaler that Fakes Fluent and Faithful Speech with Flow Matching\narXiv: 2410.06885\nAuthors: Yushen Chen, Zhikang Niu, Ziyang Ma, Keqi Deng, Chunhui Wang, Jian Zhao, Kai Yu, Xie Chen\nYear: 2024 | Venue: \nTopic: tts_vc\nStatus: reading\n\nContributions:\n  1. Introduces F5-TTS, a fully non-autoregressive text-to-speech system based on flow matching with a Diffusion Transformer (DiT) that eliminates the need for complex designs like duration models, text encoders, and phoneme alignment.\n  2. Improves text-speech alignment and model robustness by leveraging ConvNeXt V2 blocks to refine text representation before concatenation with speech features.\n  3. Proposes an inference-time Sway Sampling strategy for flow steps that significantly enhances generation performance and efficiency without requiring model retraining.\n  4. Achieves faster training and a highly efficient inference Real-Time Factor (RTF) of 0.15, outperforming existing state-of-the-art diffusion-based TTS models.\n  5. Demonstrates highly natural and expressive zero-shot ability, seamless code-switching capability, and speed control efficiency when trained on a public 100K hours multilingual dataset.\n\nTags: TTS, TTS/架构-NAR-Flow, TTS/功能-DiT, TTS/功能-多语言, TTS/控制-参考语音, TTS/功能-快速生成", "stderr": "", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
